    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">IDE Devices</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The CY82C693 provides the IDE controller, exposed on PCI bus 0, slot 5, function 1 (&quot;Cypress 82C693 IDE&quot; in <text styleclass="Code Example">show config</text>). The primary channel is the <text styleclass="Code Example">dqa</text> device path. IDE register / port behavior (<text styleclass="Code Example">0x1F0</text> to <text styleclass="Code Example">0x1F7</text> and PCI config) and absent-slave probing are part of the current device-enumeration work.</para>
